channel.title: Tornait - Songbird (EDM, Synth Pop, Electro House[?])
channel.description:
Tornait here.
I have not posted a track in a while. I have not posted on the Disco in a while. First off, I apologize for going around and being salty when it’s other people’s turns in the spotlight. I’ve been dealing with low self-esteem issues for a while, but that’s because of a lack of actually uploading content, and a lack of creative flow, especially considering I’ve been working on an upcoming EP, called Angel City. This track will be on that EP. With that out of the way, I hope that you guys here on the Disco can welcome me back with open arms, even after I acted very foolish, looking for attention and drawing it away from those who deserved it.
So, without further ado, here’s the track: https://soundcloud.com/tornait-jaybird/tornait-songbird ![image|500x500](upload://cgwlkVWmRTDp0tdwAmclwzXcOAH.jpg)
Hope you enjoy. Comments, feedback, constructive criticism appreciated. Thank you!
